T1  - Note—A Comment on Keeney's Group Utility Axioms
AU  - McClain, John O.
Y1  - 1977/08/01
PY  - 1977
DA  - 1977/08/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.23.12.1361
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.23.12.1361
